race.comment: BAFFERT (8) turned in a modest effort most recently when seventh at The Meadows over 525m behind Caly Jet (30.74) in a Grade 6. Was a winner the start prior. Was a winner at his only start from this draw. One of the main contenders. CACO MAGIC (6) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fifth (29.71) in a Special conditions race at Sandown. Has never missed the frame here from three starts. A forward showing wouldn't surprise. ESPOIR (1) can measure up with the right run. Something for the Multiples: ASTON DUTTON (3)
